{"tid":700414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川金會最大贏家，不是川普也不是金正恩","createTime":"2018-06-13T10:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T10:52:45.000Z","uid":161003,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a96d3da4ce827876fa2fcefb36d957b530b783c2","tid":700414,"uid":161003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"川金會讓美朝關係大融冰，這不只是川普個人與金正恩的雙贏，和平穩定機率大增的朝鮮半島，<span style=\"color: red;\">更讓中國在地緣政治的角力中，取得了中長期的優勢</span><br />\n<br />\n整場角力戰最大的贏家，除了金正恩超越父祖，在美朝關係中奠定了重要的歷史定位，並讓川普承諾了共同維繫金氏政權的穩固之外，長期而言，<span style=\"color: red;\">表面不動聲色的中國，可能是被大家忽略的獲益者。</span><br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，這場世紀峰會，川普贏得了面子，金正恩和美國總統平起平坐、鞏固了政權，既有面子，又有裡子。<span style=\"color: red;\">而中國則在川金會後，默默地取得了在東北亞發展的中長期優勢，可能才是川金會的最大贏家</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5090475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cw.com.tw%2Farticle%2Farticle.action%3Fid%3D5090475&d=vW5%2B4s5mdenZ%2FfTCoObt%2Bv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3799fe19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5090475</a>"},{"pid":"c92f11781c12c2ffba49a7827749af92d64d4139","tid":700414,"uid":51840,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"出現了！"},{"pid":"e847afddb154e93eba5ac4ccb8fab93b6b35504f","tid":700414,"uid":35468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69648a5dd9616399dd1554337176b895cd9a8a86","tid":700414,"uid":102948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"台灣佬又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785d647ddc2780dd23816eee4541ff038735b272","tid":700414,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"中國成最大贏家<br />\n全宇宙都知啦"},{"pid":"dd829871890898ceebb3912b73646cbdf8cb9ce8","tid":700414,